body:
@daxian-dbw 

File `https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/blob/master/src/PowerShell.Core.Instrumentation/PowerShell.Core.Instrumentation.man` contains a number of occurrences of event log messages related to "Windows PowerShell ISE" and "PowerShell ISE".

Also, "Windows PowerShell" string should be replaced with "PowerShell" in some messages.

When setting PSDefaultParameterValues for Get-aduser as follows: 
$PSDefaultParameterValues=@{'Get-ADUser:Properties' = "SamAccountName" , "UserPrincipalName" , "DistinguishedName" , "GivenName" , "Surname" , "Name" , "Enabled" , "employeeid" , "lastlogondate"}
In addition to the requested parameters, SID / ObjectGUID and ObjectClass are still displayed.
